                                <p>The Wyrd of Stromgard expansion aims to deliver an intricately themed playspace for Dungeon World that hinges on interlocking pieces that may be tailored and customized to suit every game group and play style.  Taking heavy inspiration from the Icelandic epics and the Poetic and Prose Eddas, Stromgard is a fully fleshed out fantasy realm based on the mythical cannon of Norse lore.  Players can play as legendary archetypes like the berserking Bearskin, a clever and respectable Skald, a feral and cultish Hunter, and the powerful but reckless Stormcaller.  Players can also choose to play several 'racial' classes that are immensely powerful but tempered with equally troublesome weaknesses- the Troll may be able to break down buildings with its bare fists but will petrify in sunlight and while the Jotun may be strong and powerful, they will have difficulty finding solace in civilized corners of the world.  Multiple compendium classes are available to reward characters who undergo epic journeys.</p>
